{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idaa411a75-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3901"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3901"},"text":"§ 3901.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Contracts: prohibition on competition between Department of Defense and small businesses","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idaa411a76-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3901/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Exclusion","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"In any case in which the Secretary of Defense plans to use competitive procedures for a procurement, if the procurement is to be conducted as described in subsection (b), then the Secretary shall exclude the Department of Defense from competing in the procurement.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idaa411a77-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3901/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Procurement Description","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The requirement to exclude the Department of Defense under subsection (a) applies in the case of a procurement to be conducted by excluding from competition entities in the private sector other than small business concerns in furtherance of section 8 or 15 of the Small Business Act (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s637"},"text":"15 U.S.C. 637","children":[],"tail":" or 644)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idaa411a78-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"(Added ","ch